### Add Allergen to Ingredient API Test

# Add an allergen to an ingredient
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ingredients/add-allergen
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "ingredientId": 1,
  "allergenId": 1,
  "allergenType": "Primary"
}

